---
title: Fuss-Free Cheesy Pesto Chicken Traybake with Roasted Veg, Herby Potatoes and Balsamic Glaze
description: It only takes 10 minutes to prep this Fuss-Free Cheesy Pesto Chicken Traybake, then everything goes straight into the oven for an easy dinner that gives you time back!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R45_W42_UK_R16281-4_Main_low_2-947305ca.jpg
